      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is ideal for someone looking for a project or parts car. It currently has significant mechanical issues, including a rough-running engine and several fluid leaks that will require immediate attention before it can be considered roadworthy. The exterior shows heavy wear with noticeable rust spots, dents, and peeling clear coat, while the interior has torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. Please note that this car is sold strictly as-is and will likely need to be towed from the lot.",
