      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the most exacting standards of automotive preservation. This unit remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship. Its mechanical integrity and aesthetic presentation are unrivaled, offering a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands perfection. Viewing is strictly by appointment for serious inquiries.",
